OL,3,COne of UK's most wanted men sentenced
OL,4,Cto 12 years in prison
OL,6,FOne of the UK's most wanted men has
OL,7,Fbeen sentenced to 12 years in prison
OL,8,Fafter evading justice for four years.
OL,10,FCalvin Parris, 35, from Cardiff, was
OL,11,Fdetained by Portuguese police near the
OL,12,Ftown of Boliqueime in the Algarve on 3
OL,13,FOctober last year.
OL,15,FParris had been featured on one of the
OL,16,FNational Crime Agency's most wanted
OL,17,Flists prior to his arrest.
