OL,3,COne of UK's most wanted men sentenced
OL,4,Cto 12 years in prison
OL,6,FHanding him a 12-year sentence at
OL,7,FMerthyr Tydfil Crown Court on Friday,
OL,8,FJudge Jeremy Jenkins said he could not
OL,9,Fsay the defendant had "absconded" from
OL,10,Fjustice, despite his disappearance.
OL,12,FHe said, "You did not abscond ` you
OL,13,Fwere not under arrest at the time of
OL,14,Fthe offence.
OL,16,F"However one equates it, it doesn't
OL,17,Fequate to absconding."
