OL,3,COne of UK's most wanted men sentenced
OL,4,Cto 12 years in prison
OL,6,FParris, who appeared in the dock
OL,7,Fwearing a white T-shirt and grey
OL,8,Fjogging bottoms, previously pleaded
OL,9,Fguilty to conspiracy to supply cocaine
OL,10,Fat a hearing in December.
OL,12,FMr Jenkins said Parris had been part
OL,13,Fof an organised crime group that
OL,14,Fattempted to bring drugs into Wales
OL,15,Fduring the Coronavirus lockdown.
OL,17,FThe gang used the encrypted EncroChat
OL,18,Fplatform to arrange the purchase and
OL,19,Fdelivery of drugs into the country.
