OL,6,FMr Jenkins said that after the arrests
OL,7,Fof other members of the group, police
OL,8,Fofficers went to Parris' home in Ely,
OL,9,FCardiff, but "you were not there".
OL,11,FPassing his sentence, the judge said
OL,12,Fhe had to take into account the
OL,13,Fdefendant's previous convictions.
OL,15,FParris had two previous convictions in
OL,16,F2007 and 2015, both related to the
OL,17,Fsupply of drugs, and was still under
OL,18,Flicence for the latter offence when he
OL,19,Fwent missing in 2020.
