OL,6,FHowever, Mr Jenkis added Parris had
OL,7,Fentered guilty pleas to the latest
OL,8,Fconspiracy charge at the first
OL,9,Fopportunity following his arrest and
OL,10,Fhe was entitled to full credit `
OL,11,Freducing his sentence from 18 years to
OL,12,F12.
OL,14,FParris is the final member of an
OL,15,Forganised crime group involved in a
OL,16,Fcomplex conspiracy to traffic class A
OL,17,Fdrugs into south Wales.
