OL,6,FOfficers from the NCA escorted him
OL,7,Fback to the UK on 15 October and he
OL,8,Fwas taken into custody by South Wales
OL,9,FPolice.
OL,11,FSpeaking at the time of Parris'
OL,12,Farrest, Neil Keeping, NCA
OL,13,Finternational regional manager, said,
OL,14,F"The arrest of Calvin Parris
OL,15,Fhighlights our commitment to tracing
OL,16,Fthose accused of serious criminality
OL,17,Fand returning them to the UK to face
OL,18,Fcharges.
